        </div>
        <div style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #E5E0D8; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px 18px;">
          <div style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #3D5A3E; line-height: 1;">£3,800/yr</div>
          <div style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #888888; margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4;">Wilmslow annual season ticket (approx)</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #E5E0D8; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px 18px;">
          <div style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #3D5A3E; line-height: 1;">4/hr</div>
          <div style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #888888; margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4;">Peak frequency from Wilmslow</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #E5E0D8; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px 18px;">
          <div style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #3D5A3E; line-height: 1;">29 mins</div>
          <div style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #888888; margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.4;">Alderley Edge to Piccadilly fastest</div>
